Anime Movies

Attack on Titan
In a world where humanity lives inside cities surrounded by walls due to giant humanoid Titans.
Death Note
A high school student discovers a supernatural notebook that allows him to kill anyone.
One Piece
Follows the adventures of Monkey D. Luffy and his pirate crew in search of the ultimate treasure.
Naruto
A young ninja dreams of becoming the strongest ninja and leader of his village.
My Hero Academia
In a world where most of the population has superpowers, a boy without powers aims to become a hero.
Demon Slayer
A young boy becomes a demon slayer to avenge his family and cure his sister.
Fullmetal Alchemist
Two brothers use alchemy to restore their bodies after a failed attempt to bring their mother back.
Sword Art Online
Players are trapped in a virtual reality MMORPG where death in the game means death in real life.
Tokyo Ghoul
A college student becomes a half-ghoul after a surgery and must hide his new abilities.
Bleach
A teenager gains the powers of a Soul Reaper and must protect the living world from evil spirits.
Dragon Ball Z
Goku and his friends defend Earth from powerful villains and otherworldly threats.
Hunter x Hunter
A young boy takes the Hunter Exam to find his father, a legendary Hunter.
Steins;Gate
A group of friends accidentally invent a time machine and must deal with the consequences.
Neon Genesis Evangelion
Teenage pilots fight against mysterious beings called Angels using giant mechas.
Code Geass
A prince with the power to command anyone fights against an empire that conquered his country.
Fairy Tail
A young wizard joins a guild of wizards and goes on adventures with his friends.
One Punch Man
A superhero who can defeat any opponent with a single punch searches for a worthy challenge.
Black Clover
In a world of magic, a boy born without magical powers strives to become the Wizard King.
